          a.btn.btn-outline-primary(href='#', role='button') Learn More »
      .col-lg-6.mb-4
        h2.text-primary Flexible Architecture
        p Designed with flexibility in mind, this starter kit lets you easily customize or extend functionalities. Whether you're building a small application or scaling up, it's built to grow with you.
        p
          a.btn.btn-outline-primary(href='#', role='button') Explore Features »
      .col-lg-6.mb-4
