        p Security best practices are integrated from the start, including user authentication, password hashing, and HTTPS. Ensure your application is safe for both developers and users.
        p
          a.btn.btn-outline-primary(href='#', role='button') Security Overview »
      .col-lg-6.mb-4
        h2.text-primary Ready for Deployment
        p Deploy your project effortlessly with built-in support for cloud platforms like Heroku, AWS, and more. Continuous integration and automated testing help ensure a smooth launch process.
